data.description: Come home to your very own resort! Swim in your backyard and you won't be bothered by those pesky mosquitoes and flies because this home has a screened lanai over the in-ground swimming pool. Don't want to get wet or be in the sun? Enjoy overlook the pool year round in the sunroom and raise the windows for a wonderful breeze. Sunroom has split brink floors. Fruit trees for the gardener in you! Fresh paint and carpet. Formal Dining has timeless wood flooring. Great room w/ 2-story ceilings for a very grand feeling. Wood floors and ceiling fan in Great Room. Solid wood cabinetry in kitchen, black appliances and built in microwave. Master on first floor with two large walk-in closets, in master bath, separate tub, shower and 2 separate vanities. Large bedrooms and bonus rooms provide the capability for multiple bobbies such as offices, art room, sewing room, exercise room and more! Brick exterior, cul de sac, privacy fenced yard large enough to offer you a swimming pool and there is still room to play soccer or allow a pet to enjoy. Convenient to I-10. NO POA DUES!
